file.content:
openapi: 3.0.1
info:
  description: Sample API on API Gateway with a Google Cloud Functions backend
  title: API_ID optional-string
  version: 1.0.0
servers:
- url: /
paths:
  /asset:
    get:
      operationId: get-asset
      parameters:
      - description: Contract address for the token to lookup
        in: query
        name: contractAddress
        required: true
        schema:
          pattern: ^0x[a-fA-F0-9]{40}$
          type: string
      - description: Token ID to lookup
        in: query
        name: id
        required: true
        schema:
          pattern: ^[0-9]+$
          type: string
      - description: Ethereum network (Rinkeby / Homestead)
        in: query
        name: network
        required: true
        schema:
          enum:
          - rinkeby
          - homestead
          type: string
      responses:
        "200":
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                type: object
          description: Success
      summary: Fetch details of an OpenSea asset
      x-eov-operation-handler: controllers/DefaultController
  /batch-transaction:
    post:
      operationId: create-batch-transaction
      requestBody:
        $ref: '#/components/requestBodies/inline_object'
        content:
          '*/*':
            schema:
              properties:
                tokens:
                  items:
                    $ref: '#/components/schemas/Token'
                  type: array
                network:
                  description: Ethereum network (Rinkeby / Homestead)
                  enum:
                  - rinkeby
                  - homestead
                  type: string
                recipient:
                  pattern: ^0x[a-fA-F0-9]{40}$
                  type: string
                gnosisSafeAddress:
                  pattern: ^0x[a-fA-F0-9]{40}$
                  type: string
              required:
              - gnosisSafeAddress
              - network
              - recipient
              - tokens
              type: object
        required: false
      responses:
        "200":
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/SafeTransaction'
          description: Success
      summary: Create a batch transaction
      x-codegen-request-body-name: body
      x-eov-operation-handler: controllers/DefaultController
components:
  requestBodies:
    inline_object:
      content:
        '*/*':
          schema:
            $ref: '#/components/schemas/inline_object'
      required: false
  schemas:
    Address:
      pattern: ^0x[a-fA-F0-9]{40}$
      type: string
    SafeTransaction:
      example:
        data: data
        safeTxGas: safeTxGas
        baseGas: baseGas
        refundReceiver: refundReceiver
        gasToken: gasToken
        to: to
        value: value
        operation: operation
        nonce: nonce
        gasPrice: gasPrice
      properties:
        to:
          pattern: ^0x[a-fA-F0-9]{40}$
          type: string
        value:
          type: string
        data:
          type: string
        operation:
          type: string
        safeTxGas:
          type: string
        baseGas:
          type: string
        gasPrice:
          type: string
        gasToken:
          pattern: ^0x[a-fA-F0-9]{40}$
          type: string
        refundReceiver:
          pattern: ^0x[a-fA-F0-9]{40}$
          type: string
        nonce:
          type: string
      required:
      - baseGas
      - data
      - gasPrice
      - gasToken
      - nonce
      - operation
      - refundReceiver
      - safeTxGas
      - to
      - value
      type: object
    Token:
      properties:
        contractAddress:
          pattern: ^0x[a-fA-F0-9]{40}$
          type: string
        id:
          pattern: ^[0-9]+$
          type: string
      required:
      - contractAddress
      - id
      type: object
    inline_object:
      properties:
        tokens:
          items:
            $ref: '#/components/schemas/Token'
          type: array
        network:
          description: Ethereum network (Rinkeby / Homestead)
          enum:
          - rinkeby
          - homestead
          type: string
        recipient:
          pattern: ^0x[a-fA-F0-9]{40}$
          type: string
        gnosisSafeAddress:
          pattern: ^0x[a-fA-F0-9]{40}$
          type: string
      required:
      - gnosisSafeAddress
      - network
      - recipient
      - tokens
      type: object
x-original-swagger-version: "2.0"
